title: VEC Active Vulnerability Assessment
detail: Could not resolve TLA accountId from email/query. If email lookups are blocked, provide an Atlassian Admin API key + org_id in the INI so the script can resolve accountIds via the Organizations API: 'kad.admin@vumc.org'. (Cloud privacy may block lookups.)
